body: The missing of the export symbols `sort`, `sortKeyValueInplace` and `topk` is caused by the broken reference link. It seems these header files have been referenced in `THC/THCTensorMath.h` and then `THC/THC.h`. But no file has the reference to `THC/THC.h` during the build. May I know how to fix this reference link?
